# SkillOS Package Sources
# ========================================
# Defines where to find installable Skills (agents and tools).
# Inspired by /etc/apt/sources.list in Linux.
#
# Format:
#   <type>  <uri>  <branch/tag>  [component-path]
#
# Types:
#   github  - GitHub repository (fetched via git/gh CLI)
#   url     - Direct URL to a single .md skill file
#   local   - Local filesystem path containing .md skill files
#   service - Web-based skill registry (browsed via WebFetch)
#
# component-path: subdirectory within the repo containing skills (default: root)
# Lines starting with # are comments.
#
# NOTE: When `skill search` finds 0 results in configured sources, it
# automatically falls back to a GitHub-wide search using:
#   gh search repos "<query>" --limit 10
# This discovers skills hosted in ANY public GitHub repo, not just the
# ones listed here. Results from GitHub-wide search are marked as
# source: "github-search:<owner>/<repo>" and can be installed directly.
# ========================================

# --- Official Skill Repositories ---
# These are real public repos with Claude Code / AI agent skills
github  anthropics/skills       main  skills/
github  huggingface/skills      main  skills/
github  openai/skills           main  .curated/

# --- Community Skill Repositories ---
# github  openclaw/skills          main  skills/    # Disabled: not yet a real repo
# github  EvolvingAgentsLabs/skillos-community-skills  main  skills/

# --- Personal / Private Repositories ---
# github  myuser/my-skills  main  agents/

# --- Skill Registry Services ---
# service  https://agentskill.sh  claude-code  /@{owner}/{skill}

# --- Direct URL Sources ---
# url  https://example.com/skills/my-custom-agent.md

# --- Local Sources ---
# local  /path/to/local/skills/
